  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four treasure hunters uncover a long-forgotten tomb and fall, unceremoniously, into <strong>The Void</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Separated and trapped in a hostile labyrinth, they must push forward, regroup, and collaborate through an increasingly complex sequence of deadly mazes. Enemies stalk the halls, traps fill the dungeons, and survival depends on keeping one step ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no map.<br>There is no escape.<br>There is <strong>No Way Up</strong>.</p>",
